// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1675 — Mass File Rename (blackbasta)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 47771110-146c-5442-9081-4bb15277f960

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
